TY  - JOUR
TI  - Tatonnement Stability: An Econometric Approach
AU  - Allingham, M. G.
AB  - [This paper investigates the working of a multifunction tatonnement stability process in an actual economy by simulating the adjustment path of an abstract disequilibrium model in conjunction with an econometric equilibrium model, indicating that such a path is highly stable.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1972
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1909719
EP  - 41
IS  - 1
