TY  - JOUR
TI  - Indices Prospectifs Quantitatifs et Procedures Decentralisees d'Elaboration des Plans
AU  - Younes, Y.
AB  - [This paper is concerned with the introduction of input or output targets in decentralized planning processes. The process which is studied is that of Dantzig-Wolf-Malinvaud. All the properties of a "good" scheme are present when the central board designates a neighborhood of a point of the production set (instead of an exact output target) where each firm or sector is constrained to maximize an index.]
